  "description": "Sargasso Sea: the only sea with no land boundary, defined entirely by ocean currents. Seaweed that traps plastic. Almost no current \u2014 a becalmed zone. The lowest Pressure value slows all LFOs dramatically. Near-zero Turbidity. Maximum drift depth because the stillness here is deceptive.",
